citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany the APHIS Official during the inspection process at 11:35am on
Thursday, January 22, 2026. The inspector attempted to contact the licensee by knocking on the door and calling the
phone number on file. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a violation of the
AWA and regulations. Continued failure to provide access is serious may result in enforcement action.
End Section
